Nested example

Preparation:
Use prepare.py to make forcing on a fine grid nested into a coarser.
Note: This script depend on the xarray package.

Make a virtual grid extending the fine grid on a subarea of the coarse. This is done in nested_gridforce.py
Define transformations from the virtual grid to the two "real" grids.

TODO: Make a plot of the different areas.

Three simulations are possible
ladim original.yaml    # Original example grid
ladim coarse.yaml      # Subsampled coarse grid
ladim nested.yaml      # Nesting small grid into coarse

Bruk denne navnekonvensjonen p√• release-filer og resultater.
Lag en make_release som genererer for alle.
For animate, kan ha tre script, evt overlay

